source.name: Health Indicators Warehouse
source.description:
Collection of health indicator data categorized by topic, geography, and initiative.
For developers, the HIW provides access to the underlying data through the use of an Application Programming Interface (API) which is designed to present information to systems with disparate architectures and underlying technologies.
